from CityWalk in Universal City (above) to Topanga Plaza in Canoga Park, there 
sure are plenty of fountains for youth, and anyone else, for that matter. . . . 
"We live in a desert," said Barbara Piniero of Santa Monica, "so the presence 
of water is essential." See Valley Life! Page 10. 
</P>
