<DOCNO> LA072994-0048 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 065036 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
July 29, 1994, Friday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Life & Style; Part E; Page 6; Column 1; View Desk 
