<P>
Profile; Main Story 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA072994-0138 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 065126 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
July 29, 1994, Friday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Life & Style; Part E; Page 3; Column 2; View Desk 
</P>
