<TEXT>
<P>
 AIDS campaign -- Newswatch item Thursday misidentified the name of the group 
organizing a campaign that will use bus stop bench ads to get the word out 
about AIDS prevention and treatment. The group behind the campaign is the 
Valley HIV / AIDS Center in Van Nuys. 
</P>
